  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
        BOOKSHELF is an online marketplace dedicated to making book discovery
        and purchasing seamless. We connect book enthusiasts with sellers across
        the country, offering both new and pre-loved books at competitive
        prices. Our platform empowers readers to find their next favorite read
        while helping sellers reach a wider audience.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
        Whether you're looking for bestsellers, rare finds, or academic texts,
        BOOKSHELF provides a user-friendly platform to browse, purchase, and
        even sell your books. We believe in building a community where the love
        for reading is shared and celebrated.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

