            <p class="text-gray-700">
              To democratize access to knowledge by creating India's most
              accessible and affordable book marketplace. We aim to connect
              readers with the books they need, while providing a sustainable
              platform for booksellers of all sizes to thrive.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
